<refsynopsisdiv id="_synopsis">
<simpara>i3-sensible-pager [arguments]</simpara>
</refsynopsisdiv>
<refsect1 id="_description">
<title>DESCRIPTION</title>
<simpara>i3-sensible-pager is used by i3-nagbar(1) when you click on the view button.</simpara>
<simpara>It tries to start one of the following (in that order):</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara>
$PAGER
</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>
less
</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>
most
</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>
w3m
</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>
i3-sensible-editor(1)
</simpara>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
<simpara>Please donâ€™t complain about the order: If the user has any preference, they will
have $PAGER set.</simpara>
</refsect1>
